    All Classes and Interfaces

    Class
    Description
    AudioService
    Service interface for audio operations.
    ChatCompletionService
    Service interface for chat completion operations.
    Function
    Represents a function that can be used by the Groq API.
    Function.FunctionExecutor
    Functional interface for executing functions.
    GroqApi
    Main interface for the Groq API, combining all service interfaces.
    GroqApiClient
    Main client for interacting with the Groq API.
    GroqApiConfig
    Configuration class for the Groq API client.
    GroqApiException
    Exception thrown when an error occurs during API operations.
    GroqApiExtensions
    Extension methods to simplify common operations with the Groq API client.
    GroqClientFactory
    Factory for creating Groq API clients and related components.
    ImageUtils
    Utility class for working with images in the Groq API.
    JsonUtils
    Utility class for working with JSON in the Groq API.
    ModelsService
    Service interface for models operations.
    Tool
    Represents a tool that can be used by the Groq API.
    ToolsService
    Service interface for tools operations.
    VisionService
    Service interface for vision operations.
